data.description: Everything is beautiful on Blueberry! Welcome home to this gorgeous 4 bed and 3 full bath move in ready gem. If open floor plan is what you have dreamed of, then look no further. Ownership pride rings throughout as you pull up and are welcomed into the oversized foyer. Upstairs awaits the perfect space for entertaining as your living room flows right into your new dining room and remodeled kitchen. The master bedroom offers its own en-suite and large walk in closet as well. 3 more generously sized bedrooms provides the ample space your family needs daily. Downstairs the gathering space continue with an additional family room and full bath. Once outback your 3-season room overlooks the above ground pool and fully fenced yard. Do not sleep on this one, it is waiting for new owners immediately.
